images/**
# Do NOT ignore node_modules wholesale: the extension now has a runtime
# dependency (vscode-languageclient) that must ship in the VSIX. vsce
# includes production dependencies and prunes devDependencies on its own,
# so leaving node_modules unignored packages exactly the right set.
